    <item>
      <title>Multilingual Mode</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/en/docs/configuration/multilangual/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Jul 2022 08:06:06 +0800</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/en/docs/configuration/multilangual/</guid>
      <description><![CDATA[<p>HBS supports multiple languages out of box, such as English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, French, Russian, etc.</p>
<p>You can add your own translations on: <a href="https://github.com/razonyang/hugo-theme-bootstrap/tree/master/i18n" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">hugo-theme-bootstrap/i18n<i class="fas fa-external-link-square-alt ms-1"></i></a></p>]]></description>
    </item>
    
